- `apps/web/src/components/SyncIndicator.tsx` - Indicador offline

## WebGL Cleanup Template
```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  return () => {
    if (viewerRef.current) {
      viewerRef.current.dispose?.();
      viewerRef.current = null;
    }
    renderer?.dispose();
    scene?.clear();
    gl?.forceContextLoss();
  };
}, []);
```

